cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the design of a framework for deep learning inference on mobile devices, which involves topics related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), distributed and parallel computing (cs.DC), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper specifically focuses on balancing accuracy and latency, which is a common concern in mobile deep learning applications and is relevant to all of these sub-categories.
